column2: Description
A unique identifier for each property.
The type of property (e.g., Commercial or Residential).
The tax key associated with the property.
The address of the property.
Information about whether the property is part of a condominium project (NaN indicates missing data).
The district number for the property.
The neighborhood number for the property.
The architectural style of the property.
The type of exterior wall material used.
The number of stories in the building.
The year the property was built.
The number of rooms in the property.
The total square footage of finished space in the property.
The number of units in the property (e.g., apartments in a multifamily building).
The number of bedrooms in the property.
The number of full bathrooms in the property.
The number of half bathrooms in the property.
The size of the lot associated with the property.
The date when the property was sold.
The sale price of the property.
